Package me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job

Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job.DefaultWorkUnit
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job.Reservation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<DefaultWorkUnit>, WorkUnit
public class Reservation extends DefaultWorkUnit
Reservation represents a resource reservation request made by a customer to reserve a given number of resources from a provider.
Author:
Marcos Dias de Assuncao
